WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 26=

01:45.380 --> 01:46.220
Stop!

01:49.490 --> 01:50.330
Zhao,

01:50.330 --> 01:51.170
move aside.

01:52.570 --> 01:53.410
Zhao.

01:53.540 --> 01:54.500
What are you doing here?

01:55.260 --> 01:56.820
Master, don't kill him.

02:00.380 --> 02:01.220
Wenxun,

02:01.540 --> 02:02.380
put down the sword.

02:08.850 --> 02:09.890
No need to say anything.

02:11.290 --> 02:12.130
I trust you.

02:12.690 --> 02:13.530
Leave now.

02:21.890 --> 02:22.730
Mu Qingyan.

02:23.660 --> 02:24.500
Mu Qingyan.

02:36.130 --> 02:36.970
Zhao,

02:49.690 --> 02:50.610
I thought

02:53.130 --> 02:54.770
I'd never see you again.

02:54.780 --> 02:59.690
♪Would there be no longing♪

03:00.770 --> 03:02.960
♪In that fleeting moment♪

03:03.730 --> 03:06.300
♪Within this lifetime♪

03:06.570 --> 03:07.410
Go.

03:07.430 --> 03:12.330
♪We already brushed past
countless times♪

03:12.340 --> 03:13.180
Zhao,

03:15.170 --> 03:16.060
I didn't lie to you.

03:18.100 --> 03:19.410
That wasn't my father.

03:20.470 --> 03:22.760
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

03:22.760 --> 03:27.060
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

03:28.540 --> 03:29.660
Stop your lies!

03:29.660 --> 03:33.720
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

03:34.000 --> 03:36.470
♪After parting♪

03:36.570 --> 03:37.410
Stop!

03:37.410 --> 03:39.200
♪Before death♪

03:39.260 --> 03:40.850
What exactly do you want?

03:41.690 --> 03:42.940
This has nothing to do with him.

03:44.130 --> 03:44.970
Let him go.

03:54.610 --> 03:55.450
Master,

03:55.660 --> 03:56.570
please let him go.

03:56.820 --> 03:57.660
What are you doing?

03:57.980 --> 03:58.820
Get up.

03:58.820 --> 04:00.540
Please, Master.

04:00.850 --> 04:02.290
Zhao, what are you doing?

04:03.100 --> 04:03.940
Zhao,

04:05.130 --> 04:06.260
don't beg him.

04:06.482 --> 04:08.170
He's the Young Master
of the demonic sect.

04:08.170 --> 04:09.380
I can't release him.

04:10.010 --> 04:11.100
Don't beg him.

04:14.340 --> 04:15.180
- Don't.
- Zhao.

04:16.050 --> 04:16.900
Don't go over there.

04:21.050 --> 04:21.890
Let me go.

04:25.200 --> 04:27.370
♪In dreams♪

04:27.920 --> 04:29.850
♪I become a sleeping lotus♪

04:29.930 --> 04:30.770
Zhao.

04:31.690 --> 04:33.880
♪Before awakening♪

04:34.140 --> 04:37.780
♪I have already lost sleep♪

04:38.200 --> 04:40.640
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

04:40.640 --> 04:44.860
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

04:45.350 --> 04:47.210
♪With sandstorms filling the sky♪

04:47.210 --> 04:50.340
♪I can still recognize your face♪

04:50.460 --> 04:51.370
You...

04:51.370 --> 04:52.210
Zhao!

04:52.340 --> 04:53.340
Put down the sword!

04:56.050 --> 04:56.890
Master,

04:58.050 --> 04:59.700
will you release him or not?

05:03.970 --> 05:11.200
♪I only wish to remember your face♪

05:18.850 --> 05:19.690
Zhao,

05:20.730 --> 05:21.810
you can't save him.

05:30.580 --> 05:31.900
(We love without doubt)

05:32.140 --> 05:33.660
Pingshu's hairpin.

05:45.850 --> 05:47.850
Take Mu Qingyan into custody first.

05:48.490 --> 05:49.980
Assign guards to watch him.

06:06.050 --> 06:08.610
When the stars and moon are at peace,
and the world is calm,

06:09.850 --> 06:11.140
the wedding will proceed at once.

06:11.700 --> 06:12.970
Cai Pingshu.

06:15.010 --> 06:15.930
Mu Zhengyang.

06:17.660 --> 06:18.660
Who is Mu Zhengyang?

06:19.540 --> 06:21.100
Hair intertwined,

06:22.100 --> 06:24.100
(Cai Pingshu, Mu Zhengyang)
we love without doubt.

06:28.730 --> 06:30.340
I see.

06:30.700 --> 06:31.540
Zhou,

06:32.490 --> 06:34.100
you can't blame Pingshu for this.

06:34.810 --> 06:37.580
She met him after your betrothal
was broken.

06:38.340 --> 06:39.370
At first,

06:39.370 --> 06:41.610
when Mu appeared,

06:42.220 --> 06:43.970
he looked refined and proper,

06:44.900 --> 06:45.980
with profound cultivation

06:46.490 --> 06:48.060
and a bold, carefree nature.

06:48.810 --> 06:50.410
Even I felt

06:50.410 --> 06:52.220
he was worth befriending.

06:52.220 --> 06:53.220
However...

06:55.050 --> 06:55.890
Zhou,

06:56.340 --> 06:57.980
it has been a long time.

06:58.810 --> 06:59.850
Dwelling on it is useless.

07:02.020 --> 07:02.900
How about

07:02.920 --> 07:04.370
we discuss the present?

07:04.370 --> 07:05.290
It seems

07:05.310 --> 07:06.700
the skin-painted demon

07:06.700 --> 07:08.100
is indeed not Mu Zhengming,

07:08.770 --> 07:10.716
so Mu Qingyan isn't
the skin-painted demon's son.

07:11.370 --> 07:12.210
Why not

07:13.980 --> 07:15.170
show mercy

07:15.170 --> 07:16.010
where possible?

07:16.700 --> 07:17.540
That won't do.

07:18.140 --> 07:19.580
Pingshu can't die in vain.

07:21.050 --> 07:22.363
As long as he bears the Mu name,

07:23.050 --> 07:24.980
he must pay the price.

07:24.980 --> 07:25.850
You want to kill him?

07:28.290 --> 07:29.223
I think that is unwise.

07:29.930 --> 07:31.610
He's the Young Master
of the demonic sect.

07:32.140 --> 07:33.370
If he dies in Qingque Sect,

07:33.930 --> 07:35.700
the demonic sect will never let it go.

07:36.220 --> 07:37.060
When that happens,

07:37.660 --> 07:39.050
war will reignite,

07:39.660 --> 07:41.153
and Jianghu will lose its peace again.

07:42.340 --> 07:43.580
I'm also worried about Zhao.

07:44.140 --> 07:45.580
Did you see her last night?

07:46.290 --> 07:47.410
I fear she has developed

07:48.490 --> 07:49.540
feelings for that Mu boy.

08:03.290 --> 08:04.250
Where is Mu Qingyan?

08:04.250 --> 08:05.090
The Discipline Hall.

08:05.176 --> 08:06.206
His life is not in danger.

08:06.250 --> 08:07.230
I want to see him myself.

08:08.580 --> 08:09.420
Milady!

08:09.930 --> 08:10.883
Master has given orders.

08:11.140 --> 08:11.980
Move aside.

08:11.980 --> 08:12.820
Zhao.

08:14.700 --> 08:15.700
Are you stopping me too?

08:16.050 --> 08:17.580
This has already blown up.

08:17.580 --> 08:18.700
The Six Sects are all here.

08:18.700 --> 08:19.780
Everyone is watching you.

08:19.780 --> 08:21.290
You must not wander off now.

08:21.290 --> 08:22.850
Master asked us to stop you

08:22.850 --> 08:24.020
to protect you.

08:28.900 --> 08:30.353
Let Master and the others handle it.

08:31.610 --> 08:32.550
What do you want to eat?

08:32.700 --> 08:33.540
I'll bring it to you.

08:39.180 --> 08:40.250
What?

08:40.250 --> 08:42.530
Nie Zhe has reclaimed
Bliss Palace so soon?

08:42.530 --> 08:44.180
Can you not be so agitated?

08:44.180 --> 08:45.100
Come on.

08:45.100 --> 08:46.340
I heard Mu Qingyan

08:46.340 --> 08:47.220
refused all advice

08:47.220 --> 08:48.820
and insisted on coming here,

08:48.820 --> 08:50.480
even falling out with his subordinates.

08:50.940 --> 08:54.010
His trusted aides
only defected to Nie Zhe

08:54.010 --> 08:55.770
to save their own lives.

08:55.770 --> 08:57.490
He brought this upon himself.

08:58.490 --> 08:59.490
In that case,

09:00.060 --> 09:01.420
there is no need for further trial.

09:01.420 --> 09:02.850
Just slice him into pieces

09:03.490 --> 09:04.980
to avenge Lord Wang.

09:04.980 --> 09:05.820
No, no.

09:06.370 --> 09:07.210
I don't think

09:07.519 --> 09:08.632
killing him is appropriate.

09:08.730 --> 09:11.610
Before, we feared sparking a war.

09:11.610 --> 09:13.100
Now, he is no longer the Chief.

09:13.100 --> 09:14.300
Why is it still not allowed?

09:15.220 --> 09:16.060
Could it be

09:16.530 --> 09:19.730
you have some ties with this fiend?

09:24.650 --> 09:25.490
Li,

09:25.700 --> 09:27.340
I have only met him a few times.

09:27.340 --> 09:29.530
What ties could I possibly have?

09:29.530 --> 09:31.130
If we kill Mu Qingyan,

09:31.130 --> 09:32.969
wouldn't that play right
into Nie Zhe's hands?

09:34.130 --> 09:36.010
Nie Zhe seized power only yesterday,

09:36.010 --> 09:38.300
and the news has already reached here.

09:38.300 --> 09:40.890
Clearly, he knows
we captured Mu Qingyan.

09:40.890 --> 09:42.220
He wants to use us as a blade.

09:42.730 --> 09:45.650
He hopes we dispose of Mu Qingyan asap

09:45.650 --> 09:47.250
so his position will be secure.

09:47.850 --> 09:48.770
Song is right.

09:49.370 --> 09:50.820
Whether Lord Wang's death

09:50.820 --> 09:52.420
has anything to do with Mu Qingyan

09:52.420 --> 09:53.600
is still unclear.

09:53.820 --> 09:54.770
Compared to Mu Qingyan,

09:54.770 --> 09:55.843
Nie Zhe is more detestable.

09:56.100 --> 09:57.530
We can't grant his wish.

09:57.530 --> 09:58.530
Lady Ning...

09:58.530 --> 09:59.980
Even without Lord Wang's matter,

10:00.250 --> 10:01.820
the Mu clan caused Pingshu's death.

10:02.250 --> 10:03.850
That is an undeniable fact.

10:04.220 --> 10:05.060
No matter what,

10:05.370 --> 10:06.420
we can't let him go.

10:07.250 --> 10:08.100
Zhizhen is right.

10:09.010 --> 10:10.180
When the Six Sects act,

10:10.820 --> 10:12.100
we distinguish right from wrong.

10:12.580 --> 10:13.490
If it's right,

10:13.490 --> 10:15.490
we'll do it, however hard it may be.

10:15.770 --> 10:16.610
If it's wrong,

10:17.580 --> 10:19.650
we won't do it, whatever the benefit is.

10:20.180 --> 10:21.180
That may be so,

10:21.730 --> 10:22.570
but right now,

10:23.130 --> 10:24.650
opinions are divided.

10:24.650 --> 10:26.300
A decision must be made soon.

10:27.300 --> 10:28.140
A blood debt

10:28.890 --> 10:29.910
must be repaid with blood.

10:30.940 --> 10:31.780
Zhou.

10:32.130 --> 10:33.060
What do you mean?

10:33.580 --> 10:35.370
Mu Qingyan didn't kill

10:35.370 --> 10:37.890
a Six Sects member.

10:37.890 --> 10:39.010
But the Mu clan's debt

10:39.820 --> 10:41.250
must be paid by him.

10:41.650 --> 10:42.490
Three days from now,

10:42.726 --> 10:43.995
the Six Sects will hold a trial,

10:44.060 --> 10:45.679
announce it before heaven and ancestors,

10:46.420 --> 10:48.010
abolish his dantian and meridians,

10:48.010 --> 10:49.340
strip him of all cultivation,

10:49.340 --> 10:50.490
and imprison him for life.

10:50.490 --> 10:51.940
He'll never see daylight again.

10:55.980 --> 10:57.033
I think that's acceptable.

11:00.130 --> 11:00.970
Very well.

11:01.250 --> 11:02.090
It's settled.

11:09.100 --> 11:11.140
(Discipline Hall)

11:39.220 --> 11:40.180
Mu Qingyan,

11:40.580 --> 11:42.490
you killed Lord Wang

11:43.180 --> 11:45.010
and slandered Taichu Temple.

11:45.530 --> 11:46.370
This revenge

11:47.420 --> 11:48.260
I must take.

11:49.100 --> 11:49.940
So,

11:50.940 --> 11:52.700
they don't intend to kill me.

11:52.700 --> 11:54.340
Even if they do not,

11:54.510 --> 11:55.800
I won't let you live.

12:00.420 --> 12:02.130
Master has decided Mr. Mu's punishment.

12:02.980 --> 12:03.980
Before the execution,

12:04.490 --> 12:05.890
no one may approach him.

12:06.730 --> 12:07.980
I don't want his life.

12:09.220 --> 12:10.420
I'll sever one arm and one leg

12:10.420 --> 12:11.770
and spare his life, okay?

12:11.770 --> 12:12.820
This is grave.

12:12.820 --> 12:15.100
If you truly wish to maim him,

12:15.100 --> 12:16.650
discuss with Master first.

12:17.180 --> 12:19.490
You're bullying us when we're declining.

12:19.490 --> 12:21.220
Then we will fight to the death.

12:21.220 --> 12:23.180
To preserve Taichu Temple's reputation,

12:23.180 --> 12:25.850
Master ordered us to remain silent
about Lord Wang's matter.

12:25.850 --> 12:27.490
But if you persist,

12:27.490 --> 12:29.420
the news may leak.

12:29.420 --> 12:31.820
Surely, you don't want

12:31.820 --> 12:33.180
Lord Wang to die bearing slander.

12:33.770 --> 12:36.490
I know Lord Wang was gentle
and benevolent,

12:36.490 --> 12:37.820
like a father to you.

12:37.820 --> 12:39.100
Everyone said he was a good man.

12:39.820 --> 12:41.340
But good men can make mistakes.

12:42.700 --> 12:44.300
Good men can stray.

12:46.980 --> 12:47.820
Li Min,

12:48.610 --> 12:49.580
please return.

12:59.530 --> 13:00.370
Song,

13:01.220 --> 13:02.180
you won't leave?

13:08.820 --> 13:09.660
Don't worry.

13:10.010 --> 13:10.850
Before the execution,

13:11.960 --> 13:13.320
I won't let you be humiliated.

13:14.700 --> 13:15.680
Where is Zhao?

13:16.340 --> 13:17.970
She is being watched by Uncle Li.

13:19.250 --> 13:20.090
Mr. Mu,

13:21.700 --> 13:22.990
why did you come?

13:23.890 --> 13:25.180
I promised her

13:26.580 --> 13:27.940
I'd give her an explanation.

13:28.490 --> 13:29.610
There are many ways

13:29.610 --> 13:30.596
to offer an explanation.

13:31.730 --> 13:33.530
Why insist on coming here?

13:35.730 --> 13:36.570
Only this way

13:38.850 --> 13:39.940
would Zhao believe me.

13:40.580 --> 13:41.926
You don't want her to believe you.

13:42.850 --> 13:44.010
You want to force her.

13:44.010 --> 13:45.220
You know well

13:46.060 --> 13:46.940
that Pingshu's death

13:46.940 --> 13:48.980
is tied to the Mu clan.

13:49.610 --> 13:51.130
Let alone Zhao,

13:51.130 --> 13:53.370
even Master and the others
won't forgive you.

13:53.370 --> 13:54.980
If you had not come,

13:54.980 --> 13:55.980
even with an explanation,

13:55.980 --> 13:58.250
she'd never be with you again.

13:58.250 --> 14:00.130
So, you wagered your life,

14:00.130 --> 14:01.940
betting she wouldn't watch you die

14:03.650 --> 14:04.580
and she'd choose

14:04.580 --> 14:06.300
between her sect and you.

14:08.890 --> 14:09.770
Song, how well

14:10.980 --> 14:11.820
you know me.

14:12.700 --> 14:13.540
Song,

14:14.250 --> 14:15.580
do you think I'll win this bet?

14:19.890 --> 14:20.730
Madman.

14:24.580 --> 14:26.180
To abolish all his meridians

14:26.180 --> 14:27.020
and imprison him?

14:51.650 --> 14:52.490
Zhao,

14:52.700 --> 14:54.130
you must not harbor foolish thoughts.

14:54.980 --> 14:56.420
The Six Sects are on lockdown.

14:56.420 --> 14:57.730
The demonic sect is in chaos.

14:57.730 --> 14:59.003
No one will help you rescue him.

14:59.530 --> 15:01.882
Given the feud between the Six Sects
and the demonic sect,

15:01.893 --> 15:03.683
your master agreeing to spare his life

15:03.980 --> 15:05.250
is already magnanimous.

15:08.770 --> 15:09.610
At least,

15:10.300 --> 15:11.140
he will live.

15:11.610 --> 15:13.816
He was imprisoned by Nie Zhe
for five years as a child.

15:14.770 --> 15:15.796
If he is locked up again,

15:16.580 --> 15:18.060
he might as well die.

15:27.890 --> 15:28.730
Zhao,

15:28.890 --> 15:30.220
your mother and I discussed this.

15:31.220 --> 15:32.060
If

15:32.530 --> 15:33.700
you truly can't bear it,

15:33.890 --> 15:34.820
after the execution,

15:35.060 --> 15:36.170
I'll bring him back

15:36.490 --> 15:37.370
to Luoying Valley.

15:38.340 --> 15:39.180
What do you think?

15:52.010 --> 15:52.850
Yes, yes.

15:53.890 --> 15:55.580
Luoying Valley is best for recovery.

15:55.580 --> 15:57.220
You know what I'm capable of.

15:57.220 --> 15:59.100
Though his cultivation
will be abolished,

15:59.100 --> 16:00.060
I guarantee

16:00.060 --> 16:01.700
he'll live peacefully and healthily

16:01.700 --> 16:02.693
for the rest of his life.

16:08.340 --> 16:09.490
As long as he is safe.

16:24.490 --> 16:25.330
Xingjia.

16:26.820 --> 16:27.940
Bringing food to Zhao again?

16:28.370 --> 16:29.240
Yes.

16:29.250 --> 16:31.220
She's returned it untouched these days.

16:31.220 --> 16:32.340
It feels pointless.

16:32.770 --> 16:33.610
Mr. Mu

16:34.010 --> 16:35.170
doesn't look like a bad man,

16:36.340 --> 16:38.940
but he is still the Chief
of the demonic sect.

16:39.250 --> 16:40.850
Zhao is not one who believes

16:40.850 --> 16:43.060
that good and evil must never coexist.

16:43.060 --> 16:44.770
What truly pains her

16:44.770 --> 16:46.010
is that her most respected aunt

16:46.010 --> 16:47.100
was harmed by the Mu clan.

16:48.580 --> 16:49.420
You don't get it.

16:49.700 --> 16:51.940
This time, Mr. Mu was captured
while seeking her.

16:52.490 --> 16:53.940
Zhao

16:53.940 --> 16:55.580
must be shocked,

16:55.940 --> 16:56.820
guilty,

16:57.340 --> 16:58.220
heartbroken,

16:58.730 --> 16:59.570
and lost.

17:00.490 --> 17:01.330
But tomorrow

17:02.890 --> 17:03.730
is the execution.

17:04.090 --> 17:05.860
I only hope she can eat something

17:06.730 --> 17:07.570
and get through this.

17:22.770 --> 17:23.610
Zhao,

17:24.050 --> 17:25.220
at least eat a little.

17:25.660 --> 17:27.090
Mr. Mu has not been executed yet.

17:27.290 --> 17:28.130
You can't collapse

17:29.530 --> 17:30.810
before he does.

17:31.900 --> 17:32.740
Zhao,

17:35.490 --> 17:36.810
you are eating?

17:36.810 --> 17:37.730
Feicui brought it.

17:37.730 --> 17:39.250
Xingjia, did you bring anything good?

17:43.010 --> 17:43.850
Here.

17:45.330 --> 17:46.490
Yes.

17:46.490 --> 17:47.700
Crispy pigeon,

17:48.330 --> 17:49.250
assorted duck,

17:49.250 --> 17:50.220
spring rolls,

17:50.220 --> 17:51.259
and salted egg roast pork.

17:51.660 --> 17:52.900
I watched the chef make them.

17:56.620 --> 17:57.460
How is it?

17:57.660 --> 17:58.660
The duck soup is good.

18:00.490 --> 18:01.700
But the pigeon

18:01.700 --> 18:02.540
lacks a bit of heat.

18:03.730 --> 18:04.900
That is my Zhao.

18:05.220 --> 18:06.620
Rushing to deliver food

18:06.620 --> 18:07.730
does affect the timing.

18:07.730 --> 18:08.570
Eat more duck.

18:10.530 --> 18:11.370
Zhao,

18:11.827 --> 18:12.987
it's good you've accepted it.

18:13.220 --> 18:14.060
Actually,

18:14.490 --> 18:15.660
we also hate

18:15.660 --> 18:16.980
to see Mr. Mu punished.

18:17.420 --> 18:18.860
But all Six Sects are present.

18:19.330 --> 18:21.330
He's indeed the Chief
of the demonic sect.

18:21.810 --> 18:22.810
Lord Wang's death

18:23.380 --> 18:24.730
requires an explanation.

18:25.330 --> 18:26.730
There is no room to maneuver.

18:27.490 --> 18:28.570
Don't worry, Xingjia.

18:29.050 --> 18:30.163
I've come to terms with it.

18:31.250 --> 18:32.490
At worst, it's death.

18:34.220 --> 18:35.060
What?

18:37.700 --> 18:39.010
In Jianghu,

18:39.010 --> 18:39.850
debts are clear.

18:40.250 --> 18:41.770
Mu Qingyan was captured because of me.

18:42.140 --> 18:42.980
He is proud.

18:43.530 --> 18:44.620
If he becomes invalid,

18:44.900 --> 18:46.090
he won't live on.

18:46.940 --> 18:48.770
I can't let him walk that path alone.

18:48.770 --> 18:49.620
I don't have

18:49.630 --> 18:50.570
many meals left.

18:51.180 --> 18:52.673
Xingjia, whatever good food you have,

18:52.810 --> 18:53.650
bring it all.

18:54.090 --> 18:55.490
Zhao, what are you doing?

18:55.810 --> 18:57.730
Of course, I'll die

18:58.250 --> 18:59.490
with him.

19:01.570 --> 19:02.490
Zhao,

19:02.490 --> 19:03.330
don't scare me.

19:05.050 --> 19:06.770
No need to mourn so soon.

19:07.490 --> 19:08.570
Wait until I'm buried

19:08.570 --> 19:10.770
with Mu Qingyan.

19:11.570 --> 19:13.090
Then you can pay respects.

19:14.010 --> 19:15.010
Zhao,

19:15.010 --> 19:16.530
please reconsider.

19:16.530 --> 19:17.490
Please.

19:26.180 --> 19:27.020
Hold it steady.

19:27.250 --> 19:28.220
How clumsy.

19:29.290 --> 19:30.130
Fengchi.

19:30.330 --> 19:31.170
Xingjia.

19:32.626 --> 19:34.090
We need to change Mr. Mu's medicine.

19:34.090 --> 19:34.930
Stop.

19:39.180 --> 19:40.020
What is it?

19:40.380 --> 19:41.220
Does that

19:41.980 --> 19:42.980
require two people?

19:44.220 --> 19:45.490
Of course.

19:45.490 --> 19:46.570
Fengchi,

19:46.570 --> 19:47.420
Mr. Mu

19:47.420 --> 19:48.730
is covered in wounds.

19:48.730 --> 19:50.420
It'd be exhausting alone.

19:50.420 --> 19:51.330
Go by yourself.

19:52.050 --> 19:53.140
Young man,

19:53.980 --> 19:55.050
come with me.

19:58.490 --> 19:59.420
Fengchi,

19:59.420 --> 20:00.953
didn't you say you'd practice with me?

20:01.180 --> 20:02.020
Let's go.

20:02.980 --> 20:03.820
Lingbo.

20:04.050 --> 20:05.220
Let's go.

20:05.220 --> 20:06.110
I've been waiting.

20:06.120 --> 20:06.990
Let's go.

20:08.150 --> 20:09.010
Come on.

20:09.010 --> 20:10.540
Clumsy fool. Open the door.

20:13.090 --> 20:13.940
Hurry.

20:15.140 --> 20:15.980
Lingbo,

20:16.660 --> 20:18.006
why didn't you let me expose her?

20:18.290 --> 20:19.810
Qingque Sect is under lockdown.

20:20.490 --> 20:22.506
Mu Qingyan can't escape anyway.

20:22.517 --> 20:23.649
If Cai Zhao wants to see him,

20:23.660 --> 20:24.330
let her.

20:24.620 --> 20:25.460
You...

20:25.770 --> 20:27.330
Don't you hate Cai Zhao?

20:27.330 --> 20:28.380
Yeah.

20:30.180 --> 20:31.630
But Mu Qingyan risked his life

20:32.570 --> 20:34.330
to see her,

20:34.330 --> 20:35.900
facing my father and the others

20:35.900 --> 20:38.420
without retreat.

20:38.420 --> 20:39.660
That shows some sincerity.

20:40.250 --> 20:41.690
I'm willing to grant them this once.

20:44.760 --> 20:45.620
But

20:45.620 --> 20:46.993
even if she goes in, it's useless.

20:50.380 --> 20:51.250
Where is he?

20:53.490 --> 20:54.490
You can't see him.

20:58.140 --> 20:59.010
You

20:59.620 --> 21:00.490
killed him?

21:03.250 --> 21:04.090
Uncle Li,

21:04.380 --> 21:05.490
if Mr. Mu dies,

21:05.490 --> 21:06.860
Zhao won't live either.

21:07.250 --> 21:08.860
If she seeks death over this,

21:09.226 --> 21:11.386
she doesn't deserve to be
a disciple of the Six Sects.

21:11.900 --> 21:12.900
Zhao,

21:12.900 --> 21:14.050
Mu Qingyan is not dead.

21:14.050 --> 21:15.980
To prevent a rescue by the demonic sect,

21:15.980 --> 21:17.140
he's been moved elsewhere.

21:18.620 --> 21:20.050
Don't act rashly.

21:22.180 --> 21:23.050
Uncle Li,

21:23.660 --> 21:24.660
Uncle Zhou,

21:28.700 --> 21:30.220
I only want to see him once.

21:30.220 --> 21:31.060
With you watching,

21:31.070 --> 21:32.060
I can't rescue him.

21:32.250 --> 21:33.683
I only wish to see him one last time

21:33.694 --> 21:34.660
before the execution.

21:34.660 --> 21:35.700
Yes, Uncle Li.

21:35.700 --> 21:37.420
Zhao is one of us.

21:37.420 --> 21:38.620
Let them meet once.

21:38.620 --> 21:39.900
The execution is tomorrow.

21:39.900 --> 21:41.220
The outcome is already decided.

21:41.220 --> 21:42.770
Grant her this wish.

21:42.770 --> 21:43.660
Nonsense.

21:44.530 --> 21:45.370
Zhao,

21:45.940 --> 21:47.490
I know you like Mu Qingyan,

21:47.900 --> 21:49.530
but he is not worth it.

21:49.860 --> 21:50.810
From now on,

21:50.810 --> 21:51.700
forget him.

21:54.250 --> 21:55.700
Why is he not worth liking?

21:57.530 --> 21:58.860
Because his surname is Mu.

22:03.290 --> 22:04.700
What do the Mu clan's past sins

22:05.010 --> 22:05.940
have to do with him?

22:06.420 --> 22:07.330
He's never harmed me,

22:08.220 --> 22:10.180
nor committed injustice
against the Six Sects.

22:10.180 --> 22:11.660
The only killing he ever did

22:12.090 --> 22:13.900
was when Nie Zhe drove him to the brink,

22:13.900 --> 22:15.490
just to survive.

22:15.490 --> 22:17.130
His hands are far cleaner
than Yin Dai's.

22:17.770 --> 22:18.900
He's never wronged me.

22:20.980 --> 22:22.220
His devotion to me

22:22.220 --> 22:23.220
surpasses mine to him.

22:24.090 --> 22:25.180
Why can I not like him?

22:25.530 --> 22:26.570
Why must I forget him?

22:26.570 --> 22:27.410
Silence.

22:32.900 --> 22:34.380
Zhao truly said that?

22:34.700 --> 22:37.660
Even if Luoying Valley
has always acted freely,

22:38.320 --> 22:39.760
you can't blur right and wrong.

22:40.620 --> 22:41.460
Ning,

22:41.660 --> 22:43.490
you must discipline your daughter.

22:43.490 --> 22:44.330
Why?

22:45.050 --> 22:46.660
I think my girl is right.

22:46.940 --> 22:48.090
Right?

22:48.090 --> 22:49.156
Confusing black and white,

22:50.220 --> 22:51.220
and that is not wrong?

22:52.250 --> 22:54.420
Mu Qingyan came for Zhao.

22:54.420 --> 22:55.860
And he was captured.

22:55.860 --> 22:57.330
If Zhao acts

22:57.330 --> 22:58.290
as if nothing happened,

22:58.290 --> 22:59.420
that'd be despicable

22:59.420 --> 23:00.700
and shameless,

23:01.380 --> 23:02.770
against martial honor.

23:03.330 --> 23:04.420
Luoying Valley

23:04.420 --> 23:06.980
doesn't raise hypocrites
who only protect themselves.

23:07.570 --> 23:08.410
Ning,

23:08.660 --> 23:10.180
Mu Qingyan is not like the bandits

23:10.180 --> 23:12.025
you hide in Luoying Valley.

23:12.036 --> 23:13.420
He's the Chief of the demonic sect.

23:13.420 --> 23:14.380
So what?

23:14.900 --> 23:16.330
Does that make him evil?

23:17.330 --> 23:18.660
The Six Sects are so righteous?

23:18.980 --> 23:19.900
Think about it.

23:20.570 --> 23:22.700
Wang Yuanjing, Qiu Yuanfeng,

23:22.700 --> 23:23.980
and Yin Dai.

23:23.980 --> 23:25.620
What good deeds have they done?

23:25.620 --> 23:26.720
Worse than the demonic sect.

23:28.050 --> 23:29.140
Let me tell you.

23:29.140 --> 23:30.770
If not for Qi,

23:30.770 --> 23:31.940
I wouldn't have let Zhao

23:31.940 --> 23:32.940
stay in Qingque Sect.

23:33.980 --> 23:35.660
This Double Lotus Palace

23:35.660 --> 23:37.660
was bought with Zigui's life,

23:37.660 --> 23:40.420
but I never even saw Zigui
one last time.

23:40.420 --> 23:42.530
Just let Zhao see Mu Qingyan.

23:42.530 --> 23:43.530
Is that not allowed?

23:43.530 --> 23:44.660
But the Lord has ordered...

23:44.660 --> 23:45.606
To hell with his order.

23:47.220 --> 23:48.250
If you keep talking,

23:48.250 --> 23:49.530
I'll expose

23:49.530 --> 23:50.860
everything Yin Dai did.

23:50.860 --> 23:51.980
Let everyone judge.

23:52.860 --> 23:54.730
And Lord Wang as well.

23:55.250 --> 23:56.380
We might as well split apart.

23:56.810 --> 23:58.770
I say the Six Sects should disband.

24:12.220 --> 24:13.060
Get out.

24:25.580 --> 24:26.980
(Library)

24:28.140 --> 24:29.050
Zhao,

24:30.420 --> 24:31.620
why have you grown so thin?

24:33.080 --> 24:35.140
Thank you, Yuzhi, for looking after him

24:35.570 --> 24:36.810
and sparing him humiliation.

24:37.290 --> 24:38.380
May I go in

24:38.380 --> 24:39.846
and speak to him alone for a moment?

24:42.810 --> 24:43.650
Yes.

25:13.730 --> 25:14.770
Mu Qingyan.

25:18.730 --> 25:19.570
Zhao.

25:20.940 --> 25:21.810
Does it hurt?

25:38.660 --> 25:39.620
Seeing you

25:41.330 --> 25:42.170
is good enough.

25:45.010 --> 25:45.850
Zhao,

25:47.570 --> 25:48.810
the one who killed your aunt

25:49.730 --> 25:50.620
wasn't my father.

25:51.810 --> 25:53.090
- It's...
- I know.

25:53.620 --> 25:55.140
I know it all now.

25:57.570 --> 25:59.570
In fact, I never doubted you.

26:00.290 --> 26:01.730
You only needed to send word,

26:02.250 --> 26:03.380
as you did before.

26:04.140 --> 26:05.940
Why insist on coming here?

26:05.940 --> 26:07.490
I feared you'd never see me again.

26:12.140 --> 26:13.570
- Tomorrow...
- I know.

26:14.380 --> 26:15.660
Song Yuzhi told me.

26:18.290 --> 26:19.463
After the execution tomorrow,

26:20.220 --> 26:22.180
they will imprison you in the dungeon.

26:29.330 --> 26:30.530
Take

26:31.180 --> 26:32.020
this luminous pearl.

26:36.530 --> 26:37.543
You're afraid of the dark.

26:38.050 --> 26:39.140
With it,

26:39.570 --> 26:41.290
you can at least sleep peacefully.

26:42.090 --> 26:43.420
How do you know I fear the dark?

26:49.980 --> 26:51.090
Are you afraid of the dark?

26:52.050 --> 26:53.460
- Don't be.
- I'm not afraid.

26:54.050 --> 26:55.570
You've always feared the dark,

26:56.490 --> 26:57.810
but you never admit it.

27:04.090 --> 27:05.770
From now on, alone in the dungeon,

27:06.330 --> 27:07.730
don't push yourself too hard.

27:17.810 --> 27:19.490
So, you say all this

27:19.860 --> 27:20.940
and give me a pearl

27:22.220 --> 27:23.810
just to ease your conscience.

27:28.220 --> 27:30.010
Should I congratulate you

27:31.770 --> 27:34.090
for finally ridding yourself of me?

27:37.140 --> 27:37.980
What else?

27:40.980 --> 27:42.490
What do you expect me to do?

27:43.050 --> 27:44.443
Storm the execution ground for you?

27:44.980 --> 27:46.900
Abandon my master and parents

27:47.770 --> 27:48.900
and elope with you?

27:49.630 --> 27:51.970
♪Seasons turn♪

27:53.410 --> 27:56.980
♪Sun and moon fly like the shuttle♪

27:58.940 --> 28:02.710
♪Yet why linger on what plagues us most♪

28:04.010 --> 28:05.530
Have you considered me?

28:06.010 --> 28:07.010
As I said,

28:08.290 --> 28:10.660
I'd never forsake my family

28:10.660 --> 28:12.330
and friends for anyone.

28:12.940 --> 28:15.090
When you recklessly came here,

28:15.620 --> 28:16.860
did you think of me at all?

28:17.490 --> 28:19.620
I only want a peaceful life.

28:20.330 --> 28:21.530
Why must you push me

28:21.530 --> 28:22.700
again and again?

28:26.620 --> 28:27.940
I push you?

28:27.940 --> 28:30.520
♪In the blink of an eye♪

28:31.110 --> 28:35.830
♪Unaware of when it all turns
to nothing♪

28:37.010 --> 28:38.620
From the first time you provoked me,

28:39.290 --> 28:41.140
did you think of the consequences?

28:41.140 --> 28:42.420
When did I ever provoke you?

28:42.420 --> 28:44.180
From the first time you stood before me,

28:50.106 --> 28:52.206
the first time you appeared
in the Hanhai Mountains,

28:54.490 --> 28:55.940
you had already provoked me.

28:57.380 --> 28:59.760
♪Despite grievous sins♪

29:00.700 --> 29:05.630
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

29:06.250 --> 29:10.060
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

29:13.330 --> 29:14.490
Cai Zhao, listen to me.

29:14.980 --> 29:16.700
We can never be separated.

29:17.660 --> 29:19.490
So what if my meridians are severed?

29:21.530 --> 29:23.420
Even if I'm reduced to ashes,

29:24.730 --> 29:25.660
I will...

29:27.530 --> 29:29.180
I'll return to find you.

29:30.070 --> 29:32.630
♪With a lone courage, I risk my life♪

29:33.400 --> 29:38.890
♪Wishing to share
the dusk snow with you♪

29:41.860 --> 29:42.700
You are mad.

29:43.330 --> 29:44.290
Completely mad.

29:46.220 --> 29:47.060
Mu Qingyan,

29:49.900 --> 29:50.900
we sever all ties.

29:51.170 --> 29:56.310
♪Unaware of when it all turns
to nothing♪

29:57.070 --> 30:01.870
♪When our gazes meet, our hearts soften♪

30:01.870 --> 30:06.600
♪Like clouds over a vast blue sky♪

30:08.730 --> 30:14.030
♪Scheming for the world
with reckless valor♪

30:14.730 --> 30:20.580
♪Throwing myself into love
despite grievous sins♪

30:20.800 --> 30:25.780
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

30:26.190 --> 30:30.400
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

30:30.400 --> 30:35.980
♪Throwing myself into love
despite grievous sins♪

30:36.320 --> 30:41.170
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

30:41.790 --> 30:46.850
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

30:48.130 --> 30:50.650
♪You understand love and loyalty♪

30:51.600 --> 31:00.440
♪Yet have nowhere to seek them♪

31:10.090 --> 31:10.930
Yuzhi,

31:11.140 --> 31:11.980
why are you here?

31:12.580 --> 31:13.620
I've been looking for you.

31:16.330 --> 31:17.170
What's wrong?

31:22.090 --> 31:23.390
Since childhood,

31:23.490 --> 31:24.690
I've never seen you like this.

31:25.210 --> 31:27.810
Are you worried that Zhao will act?

31:29.680 --> 31:31.230
Mu Qingyan once saved Zhao.

31:31.570 --> 31:33.620
She'll never watch him be crippled.

31:33.620 --> 31:35.770
Lord Wang's death
has nothing to do with him.

31:35.770 --> 31:36.736
He doesn't deserve this.

31:36.980 --> 31:38.090
If I plead for mercy,

31:38.420 --> 31:40.180
will Master retract his order?

31:40.180 --> 31:43.090
You are already speaking for Mu Qingyan.

31:43.090 --> 31:44.250
If Zhao asks you

31:44.250 --> 31:46.180
to help rescue him later,

31:46.180 --> 31:47.220
will you agree?

31:49.220 --> 31:52.010
Zhao cares about Master
and Luoying Valley's reputation.

31:52.010 --> 31:52.980
She may plead,

31:53.163 --> 31:54.330
but she won't act recklessly.

31:54.330 --> 31:55.660
You

31:55.660 --> 31:57.860
have been held back by your mother.

31:57.860 --> 32:00.220
You always calculate before acting.

32:00.810 --> 32:01.730
I was young once too.

32:02.530 --> 32:04.090
How many youths

32:04.090 --> 32:06.010
weigh every gain and loss before moving?

32:10.290 --> 32:11.380
What do you mean?

32:12.940 --> 32:14.010
Mark my words.

32:14.210 --> 32:16.090
Without a great upheaval,

32:16.090 --> 32:17.700
Zhao won't easily

32:17.700 --> 32:19.250
give up on that Mu boy.

32:20.010 --> 32:22.570
Whether she takes after her aunt

32:22.570 --> 32:23.570
or Ning Xiaofeng,

32:24.420 --> 32:26.010
she won't accept fate so readily.

32:26.730 --> 32:28.180
The one she loves is to be crippled,

32:28.940 --> 32:30.860
yet she neither fiercely resists

32:30.860 --> 32:32.900
nor curses us and weeps.

32:34.380 --> 32:35.220
It's too strange.

32:35.860 --> 32:36.700
Son,

32:37.860 --> 32:39.480
you must listen to me this time.

32:40.140 --> 32:42.490
No matter what happens tomorrow,

32:42.490 --> 32:44.330
you must not intervene.

32:47.220 --> 32:48.060
Song,

32:49.180 --> 32:50.660
do you think I'll win this bet?

33:32.250 --> 33:33.956
This is the first Chief
of the demonic sect

33:34.620 --> 33:36.490
in 200 years

33:36.490 --> 33:38.220
to be tried at Qingque Sect.

33:39.220 --> 33:40.860
Everyone, stay alert.

33:41.860 --> 33:43.213
Guard against demonic sect members

33:43.860 --> 33:44.940
attempting a rescue.

33:45.050 --> 33:45.900
Yes.

33:56.570 --> 33:58.380
A cup of tea in the morning

33:58.380 --> 33:59.900
brings long life and blessings.

34:09.740 --> 34:10.740
Zhao,

34:10.740 --> 34:12.490
if you have something on your mind,

34:12.490 --> 34:13.860
don't bottle it up.

34:13.860 --> 34:15.570
As long as we can do it,

34:15.570 --> 34:17.010
we will do it for you.

34:17.010 --> 34:18.420
Yes, your mother is right.

34:21.570 --> 34:22.836
I want to witness the execution.

34:24.380 --> 34:25.570
Witness it?

34:30.090 --> 34:31.860
I only want to see him one last time.

34:32.690 --> 34:33.900
After it ends,

34:35.340 --> 34:36.610
I'll return to Luoying Valley

34:36.980 --> 34:37.980
with you two

34:38.940 --> 34:39.940
and never see him again.

34:46.940 --> 34:47.980
It's right to see him off.

34:50.740 --> 34:51.650
I'll take you.

34:57.570 --> 34:58.410
Lord Song.

35:00.340 --> 35:01.180
Lord Yang.

35:02.780 --> 35:03.620
Have you heard?

35:03.980 --> 35:04.820
What?

35:05.130 --> 35:07.510
Luoying Valley intends to take
Mu Qingyan for recuperation.

35:08.380 --> 35:09.740
In my view, only by imprisoning him

35:09.740 --> 35:11.570
in Siqi Sect is it fair.

35:12.530 --> 35:13.820
Don't take offense.

35:14.490 --> 35:15.340
Your sects

35:15.650 --> 35:17.380
all have ties with this fiend.

35:17.900 --> 35:19.980
Only Siqi Sect is impartial.

35:20.490 --> 35:21.820
I must reason with Lord Qi.

35:27.740 --> 35:28.780
Little skill,

35:29.740 --> 35:31.260
but great ambition.

35:31.260 --> 35:32.780
Impartial?

35:32.780 --> 35:34.610
He only covets the Mu clan's

35:34.610 --> 35:37.010
secret manuals and treasures.

35:37.010 --> 35:38.380
Has he not considered

35:38.380 --> 35:40.650
why I didn't insist
on detaining him at Guangtian Sect?

35:41.650 --> 35:44.820
The Mu clan
has ruled Li Sect for 200 years.

35:44.820 --> 35:46.940
Mu Qingyan is a hot potato.

35:47.740 --> 35:49.300
Wherever he is held,

35:49.300 --> 35:51.050
trouble will follow.

35:51.940 --> 35:52.780
Father,

35:53.650 --> 35:55.780
don't you find this strange?

35:55.780 --> 35:57.380
Mu Qingyan was captured only days ago,

35:57.380 --> 35:59.059
yet Nie Zhe
has already reclaimed Li Sect.

35:59.570 --> 36:00.940
It's too fast.

36:04.420 --> 36:06.260
Based on my hard-won experience

36:06.260 --> 36:08.690
fighting the demonic sect for decades,

36:09.570 --> 36:10.860
it's indeed suspicious.

36:16.260 --> 36:17.260
Uncle Zhou.

36:24.300 --> 36:25.170
Zhao?

36:28.690 --> 36:29.530
Let's go.

36:30.940 --> 36:31.900
You go ahead.

36:35.490 --> 36:36.750
You are here to witness as well?

36:38.300 --> 36:39.490
To see him off one last time.

36:40.860 --> 36:41.700
That is fine.

36:43.780 --> 36:44.620
Uncle Zhou,

36:45.820 --> 36:47.690
I spoke rashly yesterday.

36:47.690 --> 36:49.130
Please don't take it to heart.

36:50.300 --> 36:51.940
Aunt often told me

36:51.940 --> 36:54.050
that at Peiqiong Manor,

36:54.250 --> 36:56.290
you taught her to write
and practice martial arts.

36:56.780 --> 36:59.490
I wonder

37:00.440 --> 37:01.980
what she was like there.

37:07.090 --> 37:08.830
She was your fiancée.

37:09.210 --> 37:10.210
Poor thing.

37:10.210 --> 37:11.340
Her parents were gone,

37:11.820 --> 37:13.980
leaving her and her brother behind.

37:31.530 --> 37:32.633
This is the MoonLake,

37:32.644 --> 37:33.690
created by the fourth lord

37:33.690 --> 37:36.130
while walking by the lake with his wife.

37:36.530 --> 37:38.530
It means two shadows by the lake,

37:39.010 --> 37:41.010
two hearts in harmony under the moon.

37:42.860 --> 37:44.130
Pingshu, what is wrong?

37:44.130 --> 37:46.050
You grasp
even the hardest moves at once.

37:46.490 --> 37:48.650
Why can't you master

37:48.849 --> 37:50.243
such a simple move as the MoonLake?

37:54.050 --> 37:55.260
MoonLake...

37:56.570 --> 37:57.410
Pingshu,

37:58.090 --> 37:59.690
Mother only pitied Cousin Min.

37:59.690 --> 38:01.130
Why argue with her?

38:13.090 --> 38:14.276
Let's break off the betrothal.

38:17.940 --> 38:19.420
Zhou, take care.

38:25.340 --> 38:27.300
Later, when war broke out,

38:27.300 --> 38:28.980
she devoted herself
to eradicating fiends.

38:29.980 --> 38:31.490
I seldom saw her again.

38:32.340 --> 38:33.180
Uncle Zhou,

38:34.340 --> 38:36.420
in Aunt's heart,

38:36.420 --> 38:38.570
you were not without weight.

38:41.740 --> 38:42.580
I know.

40:04.561 --> 40:15.221
=Generation to Generation=

